        This method reads in details about an event, and creates it
        Parameters:
        eventType - the type of the event
        name - the name of the event
        time - what time the event begins
        duration - how long the event is
        roomNumber - the room number where the event is taking place
        capacity - the capacity of the event
        requiredComputers - number of computers required for the event
        requiredProjector - if a projector is required for the event
        requiredChairs - number of required chairs for the event
        requiredTables - number of required tables for the event
        creators - the creators associated with the event
        vipEvent - if the event is a vip event or not
        speaker - the speaker associated with the event
        speakers - the speakers associated with the event
        tag - the tag associated with the event
        Returns:
        an Event with the specified details
